animeDescription: The 3rd continuation of NTV's ZIP! anime parody shorts. This one focuses on Hakushon Daimaou. Like with the previous season, occasionally the Gatchaman team and now the Mazinger Z team show up in some episodes.
animeRelated: ['Alternative version: Hakushon Daimaou', 'Prequel: Mazinger ZIP!', 'Sequel: Good Morning!!! Doronjo']
